name: Cogs120 karpool
tagline: An application we are making for our COGS 120/CSE 170 class about exploration. We decided to make an app that lets you carpool with other people to go to places you've never been to and want to explore.
body:
# COGS120_Karpool
An application we are making for our COGS 120/CSE 170 class about exploration. We decided to make an app that lets you carpool with other people to go to places you've never been to and want to explore.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
